      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHARP INTEREST (9) is in good form and added to a string of wins and placings when missing by just a head as runner-up last week at Melton. Came from a wide barrier to win over this distance the last time she raced here last month. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Leading hope. LOMBOK (2) is going well having come from tougher barriers to win her last two outings at this circuit and distance. A good draw gives her the chance to land the hat trick. OUR REBEL YELL (3) looks close to a win after clocking in second in his last three outings here, going under narrowly at his last couple. Player again from a good draw. SCHEMING (1) has claims off a second from this barrier here two back.",
